1634,NULL,'','97/05.mp3',0,'','But they speak it in school, right? Maybe they just didn’t like me so they didn’twant to talk to me.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:09:33','2016-12-02 15:21:02','lessons','','',264,'','',5,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1635,NULL,'','97/06.mp3',0,'','No, actually they liked you a lot. They told me they thought you were very nice. They are just shy. They’re not use to talking with foreigners. I remember when I first came to theUS. I was really nervous about speaking with people.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:09:58','2016-12-02 15:21:06','lessons','','',264,'','',6,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1636,NULL,'','97/07.mp3',0,'','I see. I thought there were lots of Americans teaching English in your country.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:10:12','2016-12-02 15:21:12','lessons','','',264,'','',7,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1637,NULL,'','97/08.mp3',0,'','Yes, that’s true. There are probably twice as many now as there were five years ago, but they are mostly in the cities. My family lives in the country.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:10:29','2016-12-02 15:21:31','lessons','','',264,'','',8,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1638,NULL,'','97/09.mp3',0,'','I wonder why. Personally I prefer the country to the city. It’s so quiet and peaceful.If I were to teach, I would want to teach in the country.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:10:46','2016-12-02 15:21:36','lessons','','',264,'','',9,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1639,NULL,'','97/10.mp3',0,'','Do you think you would want to teach someday? I know the schools around my town are looking for teachers, so if you want, I can call them and get more information.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:11:02','2016-12-02 15:21:42','lessons','','',264,'','',10,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1640,NULL,'','97/11.mp3',0,'','No, I don’t think so. I would need to stay there for a year, and I don’t think I cantake that much time off work.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:11:18','2016-12-02 15:21:50','lessons','','',264,'','',11,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1641,NULL,'','97/12.mp3',0,'','Well, if you change your mind, let me know. I think you would be a really great teacher.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:11:34','2016-12-02 15:21:55','lessons','','',264,'','',12,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1642,NULL,'','98/01.mp3',0,'','Dorothy, what are your plans for Christmas?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:12:26','2016-12-02 15:22:37','lessons','','',265,'','',1,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1643,NULL,'','98/02.mp3',0,'','Oh yes, it’s almost Christmas, isn’t it? I’m not sure what I’ll be doing then.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:12:38','2016-12-02 15:22:44','lessons','','',265,'','',2,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1644,NULL,'','98/03.mp3',0,'','Well, if you don’t have any plans, you family could have dinner at my house.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:12:50','2016-12-02 15:22:51','lessons','','',265,'','',3,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1645,NULL,'','98/04.mp3',0,'','That’s very nice of you, thanks. Have you finished your shopping yet?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:13:02','2016-12-02 15:22:59','lessons','','',265,'','',4,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1646,NULL,'','98/05.mp3',0,'','No, I still have to do that. I think I’ll go to the mall this weekend.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:13:15','2016-12-02 15:23:05','lessons','','',265,'','',5,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1647,NULL,'','98/06.mp3',0,'','It’s going to be really crowded at the mall. You should shop online.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:13:35','2016-12-02 15:23:16','lessons','','',265,'','',6,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1648,NULL,'','98/07.mp3',0,'','You’re right. My family loves to read, so I can probably get them all presents fromAmazon.com.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:13:49','2016-12-02 15:23:22','lessons','','',265,'','',7,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1649,NULL,'','98/08.mp3',0,'','What do you think you’ll get for your wife?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:14:00','2016-12-02 15:23:27','lessons','','',265,'','',8,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1650,NULL,'','98/09.mp3',0,'','Probably a romance novel. It seems like she’s always reading one of those.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:14:18','2016-12-02 15:23:36','lessons','','',265,'','',9,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1651,NULL,'','98/10.mp3',0,'','Don’t you think you should get her something a little more expensive, like jewelry or maybe a new computer?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:14:29','2016-12-02 15:23:42','lessons','','',265,'','',10,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1652,NULL,'','98/11.mp3',0,'','Maybe you’re right. It’s hard buying gifts. I think my wife has everything shewants. Maybe I should just ask her.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:14:43','2016-12-02 15:23:50','lessons','','',265,'','',11,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1653,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','Martin, who are you going to vote for?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:16:24','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',1,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1654,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','You mean for president?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:16:34','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',2,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1655,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','Yes.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:16:49','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',3,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1656,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','I’m not sure yet.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:17:04','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',4,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1657,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','You should make up your mind soon. The election is next month.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:17:14','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',5,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1658,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','Yes, I know. I hear about it every day on the news.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:17:25','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',6,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1659,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','I’m going to vote for Obama.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:17:35','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',7,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1660,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','I think he is a good choice, but I think McCain would make a good president also.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:17:46','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',8,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1661,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','I know. They’re both good. It’s hard to decide. McCain is older but he has moreexperience. Obama seems to have a lot of good ideas, but some people say he wants to raise taxes.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:18:06','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',9,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1662,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','I heard he wants to lower taxes. It’s hard to know what the truth is. That’s the reason I really don’t pay attention to politics.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:18:23','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',10,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1663,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','Yes, it can be frustrating, but it’s important and it’s interesting to watch.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:18:37','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',266,'','',11,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1664,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','Hey John, can I talk to you for a minute?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:19:33','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',1,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1665,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','Sure, what’s up?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:19:43','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',2,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1666,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','I wanted to let you know about a book club I joined a couple months ago. I knowyou do a lot of reading so I thought you might want to come with me next month.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:19:57','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',3,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1667,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','Oh, that sounds like fun. When does the group meet?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:20:09','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',4,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1668,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','Usually the last Saturday of the month at 9:30 in the evening. Is that too late foryou?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:20:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',5,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1669,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','No, I think that’s ok. What do you talk about in the group?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:20:34','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',6,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1670,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','Well, every month we choose a new book and then during the next meeting wediscuss it.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:20:57','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',7,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1671,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','What book are you reading now?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:21:09','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',8,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1672,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','The Kite Runner.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:21:20','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',9,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1673,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','I’ve heard that’s a good book. What’s it about?','',1,'2016-11-17 17:21:31','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',10,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1674,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','It is a good book. I’m almost finished. The book is about a boy who grows up inAfghanistanduring the 1980s. It’s called the Kite Runner because the maincharacter takes part in a kite flying competition.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:21:48','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',11,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1675,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','That sounds really interesting. I’d love to come.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:22:03','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',12,'','','','','','','',1,2,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0),(1676,NULL,'','file.mp3',0,'','Ok, great. The next meeting isn’t for another two weeks, so you still have time toread the book.','',1,'2016-11-17 17:22:14','0000-00-00 00:00:00','lessons','','',267,'','',13,'','','','','','','',1,1,0,0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,0,0,0,0);
